Template for a Django project.

Simply clone this repository to create your new project
    git clone https://github.com/suriya/django-project-template.git new-fancy-project.git

The template comes with
* A requirements.txt file to get your virtualenv started (instructions in README.deploy)
* Sqlite DB defined for DEBUG mode
* static/ and media/ directories
* A myproject/templates/ directory for global templates, with a base.html file.
